import React from "react";
import { Container, Row, Col, Card, Image , Form , } from "react-bootstrap";
import Logo from "./assets/img/logo-with-out-bg.png";

export default function App() {
  return (
    <Container fluid>
      <Row style={{ height: "100px" }}></Row>
      <Row>
        <Col></Col>
        <Col>
          <Card>
            <Card.Body className="text-center">
              <Image src={Logo} style={{ width: "100px" }} rounded />
              <Card.Title className="text-center">Namaz Tracker</Card.Title>
            </Card.Body>

            <Card.Body>
              <Form>
                <Form.Group controlId="formBasicEmail">
                  <Form.Label>Email address</Form.Label>
                  <Form.Control type="email" placeholder="Enter email" />
                  <Form.Text className="text-muted">
                    We'll never share your email with anyone else.
                  </Form.Text>
                </Form.Group>

                <Form.Group controlId="formBasicPassword">
                  <Form.Label>Password</Form.Label>
                  <Form.Control type="password" placeholder="Password" />
                </Form.Group>
                <Form.Group controlId="formBasicCheckbox">
                  <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Check me out" />
                </Form.Group>
                <Button variant="primary" type="submit">
                  Submit
                </Button>
              </Form>
            </Card.Body>
          </Card>
        </Col>
        <Col></Col>
      </Row>
    </Container>
  );
}
